WEBVTT

00:00:00.786 --> 00:00:04.716
There is some medical news
that nobody, absolutely nobody,

00:00:04.740 --> 00:00:06.161
is prepared to hear.

00:00:06.817 --> 00:00:08.221
I certainly wasn't.

00:00:08.832 --> 00:00:12.473
It was three years ago
that I got a call in my office

00:00:12.497 --> 00:00:15.181
with the test results of a recent scan.

00:00:15.205 --> 00:00:19.116
I was 35 and finally living
the life I wanted.

00:00:19.711 --> 00:00:21.805
I married my high school sweetheart

00:00:21.829 --> 00:00:25.534
and had finally gotten pregnant
after years of infertility.

00:00:26.344 --> 00:00:28.452
And then suddenly we had a Zach,

00:00:29.249 --> 00:00:32.959
a perfect one-year-old boy/dinosaur,